text: Kamajoraharule yasako prati'uttarama thulasita bhannechanh ‘‘(ho'ina) baru (timro)’’ ratadinako sadayantraharule allahasita hamile kuphra garnu ra timro adesale usako sajhedara bana'unu nai hamro anasthako karana ban'yo. Ra jaba tiniharule sajaya dekhnechan ta aphno manama lajjita hunechan. Ra hamile kaphiraharuko ghamtima (tauka) patta halidinechaum. Juna karma tiniharule gardathe, matra tyasaiko pratiphala pa'unechan
